snippet.textDisplay:
Tbh i have a hard time understanding why these guys think city are favorites for their tie against real madrid.
Sure madrid is not as strong as 2-3 years ago but they are far more experienced than city players in the ucl
Squadwise,their best 11s are pretty much equivalent with r. Madrid's being slightly better due to more balance.
The key in this tie will be experience of big matches and mental strength in which zidane's madrid are monsters.
City's record in the ucl is also very poor compared to what they do in england.They were knocked out the last 3 years against supposed weaker teams which is not the case for zidane's madrid.
